Though any implementer can define an extension, there is a set of requirements that SHALL be met as part of the definition of the extension.

Dynamic values that will be evaluated to produce values for elements of the resulting resource. For example, if the dosage of a medication must be computed based on the patients weight, a dynamic value would be used to specify an expression that calculated the weight, and the path on the request resource that would contain the result.
